2008.— Vol. 216(2).—Р. 152
3. Eng S., Xing B., Caro I., Werther W. Selected cardiovascular diseases
in psoriasis, nonpsoriasis, and efalizumabtreated psoriasis patients // Acad.
Dermatol.— 2009.— P. 3381
