proportion of anti-TNF-naïve pts and pts with early diagnosis ( ≤ 2
years) treated with SEC achieved and sustained DAPSA-REM/
LDA and MDA than in the overall population (Table). DAPSAREM/
LDA and MDA responses with SEC were sustained through
Wk104.
