of SEC treated pts at Wk16 achieved DAPSA-REM, VLDA,
DAPSA-REM/LDA, and MDA than those treated with placebo
with a greater number of pts achieving DAPSA-REM or LDA than
VLDA or MDA, respectively. These responses were sustained
through Wk104.
