TO SEVERE PSORIASIS PATIENTS WITH PRIOR
EXPOSURE TO APREMILAST
Kenneth Gordon1, Kristian Reich2, David Pariser3, Alan Menter4,
Stephen Tyring5, Howard Sofen6, Stephen Rozzo7, Jeffrey Parno7,
