presentation of psoriasis and response to treatment in terms of
the time taken and number of remedies required. The same theory
also helps to assess the prognosis and comprehend the response
to treatment [LOH]. With the help of the evidence of these cases
we may formulate a larger study to ascertain the extent to which
classical homeopathy may be employed in psoriasis.
